Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见王之柱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fn微软雅黑}sāmekh为腓尼基文字母 对应拉丁文的X
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sāmekh复活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第二队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Banishing Age」代表人 首领 到场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 绮罗星十字团总会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想诸位已经都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 这座岛屿的天空被王之柱贯穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新藤诹访与cybody「sāmekh」进行了Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将事态引致此地步的  第三队「Bougainvilleae」的责任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是随时都有可能发动Apprivoiser的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而碰巧选在昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是我们「Bougainvilleae」的责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今最重要的事情是他的现状如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据所残存的资料来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去所有驾驶过sāmekh的Drivers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在王之柱出现后再也没有睁开过双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 与死了没什么区别 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说 已经停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 我们有必要去确认新藤诹访的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然sāmekh的Driver已经觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们绮罗星十字团也必须考虑应对之策了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是视他为敌 事情可就很棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这也算是由Everonu的失误造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就让「Bougainvilleae」负起这个责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就负责到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你擅长的游泳技能尽情展现出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:05:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 我也对他们抱有期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天社团休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 因为刚才听到你在讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在练习独角戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去喝杯咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子好像从黎明前开始就一个人在入海口做祷告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在祈祷诹访君早点醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这么要好的三人小组的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这种地方没有关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为诹访 也为和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然很担心但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很担心但是……但是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我能做的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实说不定根本不是三人小组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是两个人和一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计你已经无法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和那两个人做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起塔科特君 我与那两个人相处的时间更长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着无法想象的沉重命运的他们如何才能得到幸福？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我很难想象那两人在现实中获得幸福的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们终究无法应付自己所背负的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 自从你来到这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你们三个人那么要好之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得他们两人得到幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就存在于你们三个好友间的快乐笑容之中么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始这么认为了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来干大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓青春的讴歌吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然能来这里真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你们我就这么认为了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的救命恩人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子好像很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有像塔科特这样的人出现在这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙的cybody 我会全部摧毁的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在一定能为那两人做点什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是待在他们身边也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会有非常难受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想要朋友陪在身边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他们来说你就是这种朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他们不愿这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的灵魂深处也一定如此希望着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩都不太会表达自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也不过是岛上长大的乡下人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是和子的……和子的奶奶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候得到道伯恩印记的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找和子的话在入海口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心……不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想见和子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着天体伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到转瞬即逝的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}如今的一切都在黑白画之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启吧 电力柩！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}悄然冻结的白色吐息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}压抑在心的话语化为有形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}只有聚集那份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}才能为天空笼上光明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}被悲伤浸染的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}向往重叠的纯白色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}传递着通向未来的无限温柔的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}在无人知晓的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}等待黎明的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零空间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:13:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}满载光辉踏上旅途的我有着无可预测的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}飘舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说与sāmekh进行Apprivoiser后还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}向着天体伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}深信着转瞬即逝的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}如今的一切都在黑白画之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是昨晚战争的延续！银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是昨晚的那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访他……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}让这笑容冲破乌云
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}就让我满载着爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}飞向天空的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}各自踏上征途的旅人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}或许素未谋面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}安眠时分所见梦想的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}一切仍定格在黑白记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除外来人员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我们的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的遗迹一切都是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这个人偶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游动吧！美人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜下去了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧！Τ射线银河光束！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会又暴走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经醒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！和子 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这副打扮 要到哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏加！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在零空间里 诹访醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在宅子里找找！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须快点去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王说要让出王位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王本来就打算把王位让给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献上能解开诅咒之蓝血的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Sam拒绝了那个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王 我只想要你的那艘「银河之船」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想乘上它驶向光彩夺目的银河的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不需要王位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想要国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了小鱼的故事 我又能好好加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 国王说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾向你保证 不论你想要什么我都给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘「银河之船」就让给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 年轻人啊 「刺杀乌贼的Sam」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用心听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要启动那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有将你所喜欢的少女的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一滴不剩的 全部注入引擎里才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有杀死你心爱的少女才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就无法启动那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始那就是你的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜啊 这颗糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为人生的冒险仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新藤诹访大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绮罗星十字团为了邀请您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第一队Emperor队长的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正虚席恭候您前来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不觉得他有点儿怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年 你别靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访 诹访 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 他想使用王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回平时的诹访了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打了我是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 想死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:30.38,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:30.38,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想开始悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.80,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人の鼓動触れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.80,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们触碰到彼此的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:42.67,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　今誰を思っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:42.67,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在想念谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:50.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝子星に眺めた切ないその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:50.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过玻璃星星看到你的侧脸 让人如此无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微かな距離でも届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使近在咫尺 却也无法向你传达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:01.25,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言い訳ばっかりを束ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:01.25,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:04.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:04.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:07.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱虫だったあの頃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:07.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我如此胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:15.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れそうな弱さと向き合える気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:15.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在终于鼓起勇气直面那溃不成军的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:19.33,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出すよ 明日の扉開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:19.33,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 打开通向明天的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:23.00,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が居る場所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:23.00,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往你所在的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:30.18,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃し続けてきた思い伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:30.18,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你倾诉那份一直未说出口的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:37.47,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here in my house君が笑う 何気ない世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:37.47,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这坦诚相对的世界里 向我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:46.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞こえるその声が 私の涙強くする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:46.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的声音 让我的眼泪也变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:50.40,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:50.40,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是划过我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到和子悲伤的表情
